--setting up new project server---
open up terminal(ubuntu)
cd into specific folder where new project will be placed
mkdir name-of-project (type this format in terminal)
code .
press ctrl + shift + backtick(`)key
type 'npm init -y'
opens up 'package.json'
go down the list, look key prop 'main:' change value to "server.js"
create component file by the name of 'server.js'
begin setting up database
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
follow server set up
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
--set up te server.js---
-npm install express
-npm install mongoose
-npm install morgan
-npm install -g nodemon
-npm install bcrypt
-npm install dotenv
-npm install jsonwebtoken
-npm install express-jwt
---------------------------------------------
follow server.js file database structure
---------------------------------------------------------
follow .env file structure
---------------------------------------------